
   HMM-based Speech Synthesis System (HTS) version 2.1

Install
=========

This version is released as a patch code for HTK-3.4 and HDecode.
You can download them from 

HTK 3.4 source code:  http://htk.eng.cam.ac.uk/download.shtml
HDecode source code:  http://htk.eng.cam.ac.uk/extensions/index.shtml

After downloading HTK-3.4.tar.gz and HDecode-3.4.tar.gz, expand them as follows:

 % tar -zxvf HTK-3.4.tar.gz
 % tar -zxvf HDecode-3.4.tar.gz

And then apply HTS-2.1_for_HTK-3.4.patch for HTK-3.4 as

 % cd htk
 % patch -p1 -d . < HTS-2.1_for_HTK-3.4.patch

Finally configure and compile it.

Please refer to "Compiling & Installing HTK under UNIX/Linux, OS X or Cygwin"
and "Compiling & Installing HTK under Windows" sections in htk/README for
details.

